Calicut Tuk Tuk Tour by Tyndis ! 
Among the Tuk- Tuk drivers in Kerala, Calicut auto drivers are considered as most reliable and sincere ones. 
If you are a tourist staying in one of the homestays or resorts in Calicut or if you are in a transit break, a Tuk Tuk tour around Calicut is a must-do. To deep dive into the rich culture and heritage of this town, one needs to take Calicut Tuk Tuk Tour with Tyndis.

Tuk-Tuks (locally known as Auto Rickshaws) are a great way of seeing any town or city in India. Most of the ancient landmarks that interests tourists are tucked in narrow alleys, which are best explored, in a private tuk-tuk tour. 
Mr.Sajeev, Tyndis Tuk Tyk driver is from Calicut itself who know the roads well. He takes you to the hidden gems through the shortest route and do a great job in telling stories associated with the places you visit.  Tuk Tuk Tour in Calicut is made special with the amazing care and personalized service ensured by our drivers.

Read our blog for more details :- https://www.tyndisheritage.com/benefits-of-tuk-tuk-tour-in-kerala
